IMPORTANT — LEGAL USE RESTRICTION

This software is designed exclusively for authorised security testing.
Use of this tool against systems you do not own or do not have explicit
written permission to test is illegal and unethical.

The authors of WTSA accept no liability for any misuse of this software,
including but not limited to unauthorised access to computer systems,
data theft, service disruption, or any other illegal activity.

By using this software, you agree to use it only in the following contexts:
  - Your own systems and applications
  - Deliberately insecure training applications (bWAPP, DVWA, WebGoat, etc.)
  - Systems for which you hold explicit written authorisation to test
  - Authorised CTF (Capture The Flag) competitions
  - Authorised bug bounty programmes within defined scope

All generated exploit scripts include a legal disclaimer comment.
